340
00:16:09,426 --> 00:16:10,260
Of course.

341
00:16:10,344 --> 00:16:13,555
Awesome. Well, we have
that Facing History test on Friday.

342
00:16:13,639 --> 00:16:14,932
Maybe we can start there?

343
00:16:15,015 --> 00:16:17,267
-Yeah, sure. I'd love--
-[birdhouse snaps]

344
00:16:20,437 --> 00:16:21,438
Whoa.

345
00:16:21,522 --> 00:16:25,901
All right, who coined the term Cold War
in the British press in October 1945?

346
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:28,112
I don't know. Russia?

347
00:16:28,195 --> 00:16:29,738
