353
00:16:41,208 --> 00:16:44,795
[scoffs] I can't do that.
I don't know… how.

354
00:16:48,007 --> 00:16:49,508
-Uh! Yeah.
-Ey.

355
00:16:50,217 --> 00:16:51,093
