-It's studying, not tango class.

368
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:26,378
There's a boy here?

369
00:17:26,462 --> 00:17:29,339
Oh, you're handsome.

370
00:17:29,423 --> 00:17:32,760
What's your ethnicity?
Let me have three guesses.

371
00:17:32,843 --> 00:17:34,970
No, no, no, let's not do that. Come, come.

372
00:17:35,054 --> 00:17:38,682
Devi, door stays open.

373
00:17:40,934 --> 00:17:43,812
That… That right there
is why I'm good at school.

374
00:17:43,896 --> 00:17:46,231
I live with an army
of badgering Indian women.

375
00:17:46,315 --> 00:17:48,567
-Huh.
-My mom will threaten me with bodily harm

376
00:17:48,650 --> 00:17:50,277
