377
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,863
-It's highly motivating.
-[both laugh]

378
00:17:52,946 --> 00:17:56,658
Oh my God, I've got it.
I will be your overbearing Indian mother.

379
00:17:57,534 --> 00:17:58,827
That could work,

380
00:17:58,911 --> 00:18:01,997
but isn't it a little messed up
for you to act like my mom?

381
00:18:02,581 --> 00:18:06,335
-Why?
-I don't know, because we used to hook up.

382
00:18:07,795 --> 00:18:10,297
[Hadid] Paxton! Boy, stop.

383
00:18:10,380 --> 00:18:12,674
You know what you're doing
with those bedroom eyes.

384
00:18:14,134 --> 00:18:15,135
Oh, nice.

385
00:18:17,846 --> 00:18:19,640
What's the name of the military alliance

386
00:18:19,723 --> 00:18:22,476
