389
00:18:30,275 --> 00:18:32,277
Wait, we had a trick for this one. Uh…

390
00:18:32,361 --> 00:18:36,657
Space, the moon,
counting sheep, shepherd. Alan Shepard!

391
00:18:36,740 --> 00:18:40,160
-How long was the Cuban Missile Crisis?
-Twelve days. Ow!

392
00:18:40,244 --> 00:18:41,453
What the hell?

393
00:18:41,537 --> 00:18:43,539
You just brought shame
to your whole family.

394
00:18:43,622 --> 00:18:45,582
Why can't you be more like your cousin?
Hmm? Hmm?

395
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:47,543
My cousin works at a weed dispensary.

396
00:18:47,626 --> 00:18:51,797
Well, let me just dispense some knowledge
into your brain. It was 13 days.

397
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,340
[sighs] Shit.

398
00:18:53,966 --> 00:18:56,760
-Hey, it's okay. You got this.
-[sighs]

399
00:18:57,719 --> 00:18:59,179
[school bell ringing]

400
00:18:59,263 --> 00:19:01,640
-Yo, Maxi-Pax.
-Told you not to call me that, bro.

401
00:19:01,723 --> 00:19:04,351
No doubt, but look,
I snuck the answers to the test

402
00:19:04,434 --> 00:19:06,562
