-Nah, man, I'm good. I studied.

405
00:19:13,277 --> 00:19:15,696
What? You studied?

406
00:19:17,114 --> 00:19:19,700
Why can't you be more like your cousin,
the weed dealer?

407
00:19:28,333 --> 00:19:29,918
[tense music playing]

408
00:19:30,002 --> 00:19:32,713
[Hadid] All right. He wrote his name.
We're on a roll.

409
00:19:34,089 --> 00:19:37,718
Oh no. Short answer?
Where's the multiple choice?

410
00:19:39,136 --> 00:19:42,639
Okay. We can do this, Paxton.
You remember what NATO is.

411
00:19:43,182 --> 00:19:45,601
It's the North Atlantic
Treaty Organization.

412
00:19:45,684 --> 00:19:48,145
The North Atlantic Treaty Organization.

413
