the agenda of toxic masculinity.

455
00:22:07,492 --> 00:22:08,327
Yeah.

456
00:22:09,077 --> 00:22:10,996
Oh my God. Am I?

457
00:22:12,914 --> 00:22:15,751
Thank you for calling me in, Devi.

458
00:22:15,834 --> 00:22:18,003
Paxton, stop by at lunch.

459
00:22:18,086 --> 00:22:20,297
You can take that test again.

460
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:23,967
Really? Thanks, Mr. S. I'll be there.

461
00:22:24,885 --> 00:22:26,261
[school bell ringing]

462
00:22:27,596 --> 00:22:29,306
[Paxton] Oh, what was that?

463
00:22:29,389 --> 00:22:32,392
First rule of being an honors student,
learn to manipulate your teachers.

464
00:22:32,476 --> 00:22:34,811
Mrs. Paloma gives me
a Christmas gift every year.

465
00:22:34,895 --> 00:22:35,771
[chuckles]

466
00:22:37,397 --> 00:22:39,733
[man] Seeing Devi chumming it up
with Paxton

467
00:22:39,816 --> 00:22:41,610
was more than Ben could bear.

468
00:22:41,693 --> 00:22:45,155
[Hadid] Samberg, get the hell out of here.
You had your episode.

469
00:22:45,238 --> 00:22:49,785
[Samberg] Oh, whatever, Hadid!
Why you gotta be so possessive? I'm out.

470
00:22:52,162 --> 00:22:53,872
-What's poppin'?
-Yo.

471
00:22:54,581 --> 00:22:57,667
-I brought Tarts for my favorite tutee.
-Thank you.

472
00:23:01,254 --> 00:23:02,130
Mmm.

473
00:23:02,714 --> 00:23:04,800
